<p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px 0pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">为保障学校教学与管理工作平稳运行，4月1日下午，我校在行政楼一楼会议室召开了2023-2024学年第二学期第二次教学工作会议。执行校长范红铭，教务处、科技处、人事处、学工处、质评中心、财务处、信息处、实验实训中心、校企合作办、图书馆等主要负责人，各教学院（部）院长（主任）、教学副院长（副主任）、教务科长及教务处人员等参加了会议。傅志军副校长主持会议并讲话。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px 0pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px 0pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2016%3A02%3A18%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2027923338&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=k0K3M8KGdrAob1TN6A3GTADw0J8%3D" alt="" width="650" height="343" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 343px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px 0pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px 0pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">教务处处长李嵩就开学以来的工作进行了汇报，并对教学运行、质量工程、考试管理、学籍管理、竞赛管理、教材管理、实践教学、考研信息统计等十个方面进行了工作布置安排。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">马克思主义学院院长李玉林就</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">省教育工委、省教育厅进高校听思政课做了布置与安排。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px 0pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px 0pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-04-08%2016%3A02%3A42%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=2027923362&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=nNOaEsTCZRqsWH1on4sq3%2BOrq0Y%3D" alt="" width="650" height="569" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; height: 569px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px 0pt 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">执行校长范红铭强调教学与管理工作是一项系统工程，需要全校上下勠力同心，以</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">本科教学工作</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">合格评估的标准为导向，树立顶层设计意识，从全局出发，统筹规划教学与管理工作，确保各项工作的协调推进。一是做好教学基础性工作。树立教学质量意识，抓好教学基础性工作，对标对表</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">本科层次职业学校本科教学工作合格评估指标和基本要求，从点滴做起，打磨基础。二是突出专业群建设。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">各学院必须及早谋划，深入剖析专业间的内在联系和互补性，构建科学合理的专业群架构，形成具有特色的专业群发展格局，注重加强与企业、行业协会等外部机构的合作与交流，引入外部资源，推动产学研深度融合。三是努力取得标志性成果。高校作为知识创新和人才培养的重要基地，必须致力于取得标志性成果，以此提升学校的整体竞争力和社会影响力。青年教师是科研工作的生力军，要鼓励青年教师动手搞科研，提供充足的科研资源和平台，激发他们的科研热情和创造力。不断壮大人才队伍，通过引进优秀人才、加强内部培养和选拔等方式，构建一支结构合理、素质优良、充满活力的教师团队。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">傅校长在会上强调，要明确教学与管理工作的中心地位，切实抓好教风学风，推进教学各项工作落细、落小、落实。一是教师要做好上课准备工作，确保上课的充分性和系统性。二是要切实做好毕业论文（设计）工作，各学院要严把指导关、严把过程管理关、严把论文质量关。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important; font-size: 16px !important;">三是要做好学籍清查工作，定期进行全面清查，比对各项数据，建立学籍信息预警机制，及时处理存在的问题和错误纠正。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>